{"tid":1126302,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（多圖）今日Lunch食越棧,發覺越棧真係童叟無欺","createTime":"2019-04-26T09:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T08:43:53.000Z","uid":176960,"like":3163,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"b9efebf8ea4d64b45bba96bbd0f5f847acebd141","tid":1126302,"uid":176960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:45:12.000Z","msg":"Lunch肚餓唔想食茶記頹飯，於是就走去食越棧，<br />\n一坐底睇完餐牌就叫咗個有四個餸嘅特別牛河<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqhow2q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjqhow2q.png&h=8871d3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有生牛肉、牛扎肉、牛腩片同牛肚絲<br />\n<br />\n生牛肉正正常常無影到，<br />\n首先睇下牛扎肉<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYynNC1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYynNC1.png&h=da66f9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n薄到透光<br />\n<br />\n再睇下牛腩片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMiOJfg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMiOJfg.png&h=33b57bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又薄又細片，好似食茶記火腿通果啲火腿絲感<br />\n<br />\n最後睇下牛肚絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78ftJfP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78ftJfP.png&h=c11118e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最長果條<br />\n其餘果啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhC7YPp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhC7YPp.png&h=01abc052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食評：生牛肉最大塊，大到爭啲食唔晒～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其餘餸適合胃口細或者係櫻桃小嘴嘅人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外真係要讚下廚房師傅刀工，堪稱藝術家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a2636f25f3046a6deb1209c5ae5c1b5ed8f4c2","tid":1126302,"uid":693,"like":1418,"dislike":4,"score":1414,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:46:41.000Z","msg":"睇到牛肚絲已經笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似周星馳以前D戲既FEELING<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa